reviewText: I love this DVD set.  Two separate workouts and they both really stretch me out.
use these every day to stay in shape

I bought her machine to do pilates like 5 years ago. My husband and I use it all the time. My husband suffers from back pain, and her machine helps reduce the pain tremendously. We need this machine to move all day long. Right now I'm looking to buy another one to keep in my basement besides the one I keep in my bedroom.
